_sText:
This is the first map that I have released to the site.
I would like to start of by thanking all the people who made this release possible; My friends who helped me test it and gave me ideas, the tutorials on this site that I have followed and FPSB for letting me host the map.

The map has custom nav locations, but does not currently have a Radar, I will be working on this and I shall add it to this release when I have made the radar. 

In the map; while I was making it I decided to make every door and window breakable instead of openable as I thought that it would effect elements in gameplay and make the map less boring.

I hope you all enjoy the map.

To install this map; Put all the contents of the .zip(the .bsp, the .nav and the .txt) into;
C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\Yourusername\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
